title: Kendall Jenner goes topless
text:

Los Angeles, Oct 24: Kendall Jenner opted for another racy shot following shower shots with photographer Mert Alas earlier this month. The “Keeping Up with the Kardashians” star took to Instagram to share a black-and-white picture showing her topless in Calvin Klein jeans, reported Ace Showbiz.
